_yaml_::scanner::Scanner::indent

In flow context, tokens should respect indentation. Actually the condition should be `self.indent >= column` according to the spec. But this condition will prohibit intuitively correct constructions such as key : { } if self.flow_level and self.indent > column: raise ScannerError(None, None, "invalid intendation or unclosed '[' or '{'", self.get_mark())
